<p><strong>Requirements for Foreigners:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Valid work permit or long-term visa</li>
<li>Malaysian employment contract</li>
<li>Local bank account with salary crediting</li>
<li>Usually require local guarantor</li>
<li>Higher income requirements (often RM5,000+)</li>
<li>Limited to certain banks and non-bank lenders</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Best Options:</strong></p>
